name: Incarcerated Naturalism
description: Early edition from the series "Dark Realities' by @trnvirsingh. This artwork was created in the support against the body shaming. The topic came into the lime light in the late 2018 and artists/influencers around the world came forward to push it over social media to create awareness. Human body is one of the most natural element and it is no less than an art itself. How the society incarcerate the naturalism is how the reality is turning dark.
